# Safe Customer Claim Library

## Safe claims

- EdgeTwin prepares controlled pilot/evidence packs with data-quality checks, trust notes, assumptions, limitations and concrete next steps.
- EdgeTwin helps teams assess whether their data and use-case are ready for a controlled AI or predictive-maintenance pilot.
- EdgeTwin supports decision-making by making data readiness, risks and next steps more visible.
- EdgeTwin can use synthetic benchmarks and customer-approved data profiles to improve pilot-readiness checks.

## Avoid

- 100% accurate
- guaranteed prediction
- production-ready
- legally approved
- compliance certified
- safety certified
- replaces human review
- accepts all liability
- risk-free
